articles.title: "Rookie", "ChatGPT": Indian-American Candidate Vivek Ramaswamy Mocked At Republican Debate - NDTV
articles.description: Indian-American entrepreneur Vivek Ramaswamy was in for a lot of attention -- and drubbing in equal measure -- at the debate of eight Republican US Presidential candidates at Milwaukee last night.
